---
const wardrobeImage = '/images/gallery-mom-portrait.jpg';
const wardrobeImageAlt = 'Smiling portrait of mom leaning against the white barn structure.';
---

<section id="wardrobe" class="bg-white">
	<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] lg:px-10">
		<div>
			<h2 class="section-heading">Look Your Best â€” With Zero Guesswork</h2>
			<p class="section-subheading">
				Keep it polished and timeless with these stylist-approved wardrobe cues.
			</p>
			<ul class="mt-8 grid gap-4 text-base text-brand-charcoal/85">
				<li class="rounded-xl border border-brand-gold/30 bg-brand-gray/70 p-4">
					<span class="font-semibold text-brand-charcoal">Neutrals &amp; earth tones:</span> cream, tan, olive, denim, rust, soft gray, sage.
				</li>
				<li class="rounded-xl border border-brand-gold/30 bg-brand-gray/70 p-4">
					<span class="font-semibold text-brand-charcoal">Textures:</span> knits, linen, denim, layers.
				</li>
				<li class="rounded-xl border border-brand-gold/30 bg-brand-gray/70 p-4">
					<span class="font-semibold text-brand-charcoal">Avoid:</span> busy patterns, logos, neon, shiny fabrics.
				</li>
				<li class="rounded-xl border border-brand-gold/30 bg-brand-gray/70 p-4">
					<span class="font-semibold text-brand-charcoal">Keep hair and makeup natural and timeless.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="space-y-6">
			<figure class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-brand-gold/40 bg-white shadow-subtle">
				<img src={wardrobeImage} alt={wardrobeImageAlt} class="h-full w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
			</figure>
			<div class="card space-y-4">
				<p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-holiday">Need a deeper dive?</p>
				<p class="text-base text-brand-charcoal/80">
					Download the full wardrobe guide for color palettes, styling inspiration, and shopping suggestions.
				</p>
				<a
					href="/WardrobeGuide.pdf"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener"
					class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-brand-indigo px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-subtle transition duration-200 ease-soft hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-brand-holiday hover:shadow-lg"
				>
					Download the Family Wardrobe Guide (Free)
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>



